cs.LO, cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.RO, cs.CR 

The paper discusses the design of efficient and verifiable data structures for high assurance systems, which involves formal verification and programming language design. This makes it likely to belong to the categories of Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO), Software Engineering (cs.SE), Programming Languages (cs.PL), Robotics (cs.RO), and Cryptography and Security (cs.CR). However, since the paper focuses more on the design and verification of data structures rather than cryptography and security, cs.CR is the least likely category.
